The Financial Services Authority
fined  David Einhorn , owner of hedge fund Greenlight Capital Inc.
and his fund 7.2 million pounds ($11.2 million) for using inside
information to trade  Punch Taverns Plc (PUB)  securities in June 2009, 
the agency said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
